{"title":"Hex to hsl converter","description":"A program that allows you to quickly convert hex to hsl online.","content":"## About the hex to hsl converter\r\nThis converter allows you to convert a color represented by the **HEX** color model to **HSL**\r\nAs a result of the conversion, you will get three numbers whose values ​​reflect the hue, saturation and lightness of the color in the **HSL** model.\r\nThis program can also perform reverse conversion, that is, [convert hsl to hex](/en/color/hsl_to_hex).\r\n\r\n## How to convert hex to hsl\r\nTo perform the conversion, enter the hex value in the corresponding line instead of the current color.\r\nThe **RGB** value will be immediately calculated and displayed in three fields for each primary color: red, green and blue."}